{"id":768,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":768,"title":"Isaiah 66","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 66"],[".studySummary",["i","At the Second Coming, Israel, as a nation, will be born in a day; the wicked will be destroyed; and the Gentiles will hear the gospel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.1","order":"02.24.066.50504"},["b","1"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", The heaven",["i","is"],"my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"throne"],", and the earth",["i","is"],"my footstool: where",["i","is"],"the house that ye build unto me? and where",["i","is"],"the place of my rest?"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.2","order":"02.24.066.50505"},["b","2"],"For all those",["i","things"],"hath mine hand made, and all those",["i","things"],"have been, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": but to this",["i","man"],"will I look,",["i","even"],"to",["i","him that is"],"poor and of a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"contrite spirit"],", and trembleth at my word."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.3","order":"02.24.066.50506"},["b","3"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"He"],"that killeth an ox",["i","is as if"],"he slew a man; he that sacrificeth a lamb,",["i","as if"],"he cut off a dog’s neck; he that offereth an oblation,",["i","as if he offered"],"swine’s blood; he that burneth incense,",["i","as if"],"he blessed an idol. Yea, they have chosen their own ways, and their soul delighteth in their abominations."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.4","order":"02.24.066.50507"},["b","4"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"I"],"also will choose their delusions, and will bring their fears upon them; because when I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"called"],", none did answer; when I spake, they did not hear: but they did evil before mine eyes, and chose",["i","that"],"in which I delighted not."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.5","order":"02.24.066.50508"},["b","5"],"¶Hear the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", ye that tremble at his word; Your brethren that hated you, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cast"],"you out for my name’s sake, said, Let the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"glorified"],": but he shall appear to your joy, and they shall be ashamed."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.6","order":"02.24.066.50509"},["b","6"],"A voice of noise from the city, a voice from the temple, a voice of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"that rendereth recompence to his enemies."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.7","order":"02.24.066.50510"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Before"],"she",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"travailed"],", she brought forth; before her pain came, she was delivered of a man",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"child"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.8","order":"02.24.066.50511"},["b","8"],"Who hath heard such a thing? who hath seen such things? Shall the earth be made to bring forth in one day?",["i","or"],"shall a nation be born at once? for as soon as Zion travailed, she brought forth her children."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.9","order":"02.24.066.50512"},["b","9"],"Shall I bring to the birth, and not cause to bring forth? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": shall I cause to bring forth, and shut",["i","the womb?"],"saith thy God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.10","order":"02.24.066.50513"},["b","10"],"Rejoice ye with Jerusalem, and be glad with her, all ye that love her: rejoice for joy with her, all ye that mourn for her:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.11","order":"02.24.066.50514"},["b","11"],"That ye may suck, and be satisfied with the breasts of her consolations; that ye may milk out, and be delighted with the abundance of her glory."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.12","order":"02.24.066.50515"},["b","12"],"For thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Behold, I will extend peace to her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"like a river"],", and the glory of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"Gentiles"],"like a flowing stream: then shall ye suck, ye shall be borne upon",["i","her"],"sides, and be dandled upon",["i","her"],"knees."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.13","order":"02.24.066.50516"},["b","13"],"As one whom his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"mother"],"comforteth, so will I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"comfort"],"you; and ye shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"comforted"],"in Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.14","order":"02.24.066.50517"},["b","14"],"And when ye see",["i","this,"],"your heart shall rejoice, and your bones shall flourish like an herb: and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"hand"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall be known toward his servants, and",["i","his"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"indignation"],"toward his enemies."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.15","order":"02.24.066.50518"},["b","15"],"For, behold, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will come with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"fire"],", and with his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"chariots"],"like a whirlwind, to render his anger with fury, and his rebuke with flames of fire."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16","order":"02.24.066.50519"},["b","16"],"For by fire and by his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"sword"],"will",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"the"],["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"plead"],"with all flesh: and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_16d"},"slain"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall be many."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.17","order":"02.24.066.50520"},["b","17"],"They that sanctify themselves, and purify themselves in the gardens behind one",["i","tree"],"in the midst, eating swine’s flesh, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"abomination"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"mouse"],", shall be consumed together, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.18","order":"02.24.066.50521"},["b","18"],"For I",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"know"]],"their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"works"],"and their thoughts: it shall come, that I will gather",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"all"],"nations and tongues; and they shall come, and see my glory."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19","order":"02.24.066.50522"},["b","19"],"And I will set a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"sign"],"among them, and I will send those that escape of them unto the nations,",["i","to"],"Tarshish, Pul, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"Lud"],", that draw the bow,",["i","to"],"Tubal, and Javan,",["i","to"],"the isles afar off, that have not heard my fame, neither have seen my glory; and they shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"declare"],"my glory among the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.20","order":"02.24.066.50523"},["b","20"],"And they shall bring all your brethren",["i","for"],"an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"offering"],"unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"out of all nations upon horses, and in chariots, and in litters, and upon mules, and upon swift beasts, to my holy mountain Jerusalem, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", as the children of Israel bring an offering in a clean vessel into the house of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.21","order":"02.24.066.50524"},["b","21"],"And I will also take of them for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"priests"],["i","and"],"for Levites, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.22","order":"02.24.066.50525"},["b","22"],"For as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"new"],"heavens and the new earth, which I will make, shall remain before me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", so shall your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"seed"],"and your name remain."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.23","order":"02.24.066.50526"},["b","23"],"And it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"from one new moon to another, and from one sabbath to another, shall all flesh come to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"worship"],"before me, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.24","order":"02.24.066.50527"},["b","24"],"And they shall go forth, and look upon the carcases of the men that have transgressed against me: for their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"worm"],"shall not die, neither shall their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"fire"],"be quenched; and they shall be an abhorring unto all flesh."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.1a","order":"02.24.066.50528"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.34"},"Matt. 5:34"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"},"TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.2a","order":"02.24.066.50530"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/contrite-heart"},"TG Contrite Heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.3a","order":"02.24.066.50532"},["b","3a"],["span.small","IE"],"The same person both sacrifices and yet sins;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.9-12"},"James 3:9–12"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.4a","order":"02.24.066.50534"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"The Lord will respond to their evils and punish them."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.4b","order":"02.24.066.50536"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/65.12"},"Isa. 65:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.5a","order":"02.24.066.50538"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.22"},"Luke 6:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.5b","order":"02.24.066.50540"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/1.10.9-10"},"2 Thes. 1:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.7a","order":"02.24.066.50542"},["b","7a"],["span.small","IE"],"Zion will suddenly be repopulated (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.7-9"},"vv. 7–9"],")."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.7b","order":"02.24.066.50544"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.10"},"Micah 4:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.7c","order":"02.24.066.50546"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/12.2.1-5"},"Rev. 12:2 (1–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-rev/12.1-8"},["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 12:1–8 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.12a","order":"02.24.066.50548"},["b","12a"],["span.small","IE"],"abundantly."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.12b","order":"02.24.066.50550"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.7"},"D&C 35:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.13a","order":"02.24.066.50552"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-motherhood"},"TG Marriage, Motherhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.13b","order":"02.24.066.50554"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/comfort"},"TG Comfort"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.13c","order":"02.24.066.50556"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"TG Israel, Restoration of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.14a","order":"02.24.066.50558"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/protection-divine"},"TG Protection, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.14b","order":"02.24.066.50560"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.15a","order":"02.24.066.50562"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.12.12,21,28"},"D&C 29:12 (12, 21, 28)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.7"},"130:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.41"},"133:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.15b","order":"02.24.066.50564"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/abr/2.7"},"Abr. 2:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16a","order":"02.24.066.50566"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.41"},"Deut. 32:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/27.1"},"Isa. 27:1"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/war"},"TG War"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16b","order":"02.24.066.50568"},["b","16b"],["span.small","HEB"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will judge all flesh."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16c","order":"02.24.066.50570"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.31"},"Jer. 25:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.22"},"Ezek. 38:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.2"},"Joel 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"16d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.16d","order":"02.24.066.50572"},["b","16d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.33"},"Jer. 25:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.17a","order":"02.24.066.50574"},["b","17a"],"Several examples of forbidden practices are listed here."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.17b","order":"02.24.066.50576"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/11.29"},"Lev. 11:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.18a","order":"02.24.066.50578"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.18b","order":"02.24.066.50580"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.15.15-16"},"Rev. 3:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.18c","order":"02.24.066.50582"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/86.9"},"Ps. 86:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19a","order":"02.24.066.50584"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ensign"},"TG Ensign"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19b","order":"02.24.066.50586"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/46.9"},"Jer. 46:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/27.10"},"Ezek. 27:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/30.5"},"30:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19c","order":"02.24.066.50588"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.19d","order":"02.24.066.50590"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gentiles"},"TG Gentiles"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.20a","order":"02.24.066.50592"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.7"},"Isa. 60:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.21a","order":"02.24.066.50594"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/61.6"},"Isa. 61:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.22a","order":"02.24.066.50596"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.22b","order":"02.24.066.50598"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.23a","order":"02.24.066.50600"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.16"},"Zech. 14:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.24a","order":"02.24.066.50602"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/9.48.43-48"},"Mark 9:48 (43–48)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.44"},"D&C 76:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.24b","order":"02.24.066.50604"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],"."]]}
